{
  "id": null,
  "uid": "mycelium-stages",
  "title": "mycelium — stages",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": { "from": "now-30m", "to": "now" },
  "tags": ["lab", "guest", "mycelium"],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Stage throughput (processed/s by stage)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ops" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (stage) (rate(mycelium_stage_processed_total[2m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{stage}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Stage duration p95 (by stage)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, stage) (rate(mycelium_stage_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{stage}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Stage queue depth (km.stage.* on vhost mycelium)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "rabbitmq_queue_messages{vhost=\"mycelium\", queue=~\"km\\\\.stage\\\\.[^.]+\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{queue}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Dead-letter depth (km.stage.*.dlq on vhost mycelium)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "rabbitmq_queue_messages{vhost=\"mycelium\", queue=~\"km\\\\.stage\\\\..+\\\\.dlq\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{queue}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "About this dashboard",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 16 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Stage counters/durations come from mycelium's Prometheus `/metrics` (stages-api). **The exact metric names (`mycelium_stage_processed_total`, `mycelium_stage_duration_seconds`, label `stage`) are confirmed guest-side (KM-2)** — adjust here if they differ. Queue panels read the shared RabbitMQ exporter for the `mycelium` vhost; the `km.stage.<name>` topology + `.dlq` are owned by the orchestrator's generator (ADR-007.4). In fake mode (EXP-70) stages drain with zero LLM spend."
      }
    }
  ]
}
